               <persName>
                           <forename>William</forename> le <surname>Chapmon</surname>
                        </persName> the <pb n="405"/> whole of his arable
               land which he has in <placeName key="place_101020">Bromleg' Abbots</placeName> in a field called '<placeName type="minor">Harleyfeld</placeName>.' 
               Dated at <placeName role="date" key="place_101020">Bromleg</placeName>' the Friday next after the feast of
               the Nativity of St. John the Baptist, <origDate notBefore="1309-07-08" notAfter="1310-07-07">3 Ed. II</origDate>.
